    "description": "<strong>Day 1, 7:48</strong><br><br>You close the drawers and get the car keys off the desk. The first delivery's not far from here - hopefully you won't waste too much time in traffic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259180/extras/6d58e45598cbb29c9e839f808f741af2.poster.avif?t=1758661531\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259180/extras/6d58e45598cbb29c9e839f808f741af2.webm?t=1758661531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259180/extras/6d58e45598cbb29c9e839f808f741af2.mp4?t=1758661531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Day █, 18:32</strong><br><br>Sal pours you another Conviction, as you mentally map out the gathered clues. Visit to █████'s place yielded more questions than answers - who's involved? And why? You shrug, waving away cigarette smoke with your hand. Someone in this damn city knows something about ███'s disappearance... and you won't stop short of finding them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259180/extras/88ff48ad8045941986ad7d85b3d89e4d.poster.avif?t=1758661531\" width=520 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259180/extras/88ff48ad8045941986ad7d85b3d89e4d.webm?t=1758661531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259180/extras/88ff48ad8045941986ad7d85b3d89e4d.mp4?t=1758661531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In NQA, the mystery unfolds along your choices. You might follow the story, or simply do your job - as a Courier. The city presents you with several paths:<br><br>- branching dialogues,<br><br>- scenes reacting to your actions... and the influence of drugs,<br><br>- a number of endings and varying ways of reaching them.<br><br>However, keep in mind that time flies - and different opportunities arise and disappear. <br><br><br>Now, just your signature here: _____________",
